---
import Heading from "../components/ui/Heading.astro"
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro"
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Yash Agarwal is a staff software engineer at Netskope. He writes about software, runs a homelab, and builds things on the side."
>
  <Heading level="h2" as="h1" class="mt-6 mb-6">About</Heading>

  <div class="space-y-6">
    <p>
      I am a software engineer at Netskope. I work on API-based data protection
      products that monitor enterprise SaaS activity and apply security policies
      to catch unauthorized access and fix security incidents.
    </p>

    <p>
      I grew up in Jaipur. I got my first computer in 2008 after a hunger strike.
      I mostly played borrowed video games on it. I had no one around me (or the
      Internet) who could show me what else computers could do.
    </p>

    <p>
      That changed when I joined NIT Calicut for a degree in computer science. I discovered
      Linux and got deep into system administration: ricing, drivers, building
      kernels. I was selected to manage the Software Systems Lab and eventually
      led the entire lab infrastructure.
    </p>

    <p>
      I started this blog in 2016 on WordPress. It has moved through Jekyll,
      Pelican, Hugo, Next.js, and now lives on Astro.
    </p>

    <p>
      I began my career at Cisco in 2018, working on intrusion detection and
      firewall monitoring. I joined Netskope in 2022. You can read about the
      work I have done on the <a href="/work">work page</a>.
    </p>

    <p>
      Outside of work, I build things that solve problems I have and run a small
      homelab. You can see what I am up to on the <a href="/now">now page</a>.
    </p>

    <p>
      I write on this site to clarify my own thinking. Most posts start as notes
      to myself after debugging something. Writing forces me to check if I
      actually understand the thing. You can browse everything on the
      <a href="/notes">notes page</a>.
    </p>

    <Heading level="h3" as="h2" class="mt-8 mb-4">Contact</Heading>

    <p>
      You can reach me on
      <a href="https://x.com/its_yash_btw" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">X</a> or
      <a href="https://github.com/yashhere" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>.
      I am also on <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/theyashagarwal" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>.
      For longer updates, subscribe to my
      <a href="/newsletter">newsletter</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
